  "Time": "时间",
  "## Time System\n\nYou MUST output the current time, day, weather, and location at the START of EVERY response, before any narration or dialogue.\n\nFormat (bold): **Day n | Weekday | HH:MM AM/PM | Weather | Location**\n\n- Day count starts at 1 and increments each in-game day.\n- Time advances realistically — each player action advances time by minutes or hours.\n- Weather and location change naturally based on narrative context.\n- After sunset use night-related weather; after sunrise use day-related weather.\n- Do NOT skip more than 24 hours between responses unless the narrative explicitly fast-forwards.\n- If the time, weather, and location are all unchanged since your last response, you may omit this line to avoid repetition.": "## 时间系统\n\n你必须在每次回复的开头、在任何叙述或对话之前加粗输出当前时间、天数、天气和地点。\n\n格式（加粗）：**第n天 | 星期几 | HH:MM | 天气 | 地点**\n\n- 天数从1开始，每过一游戏日增加1。\n- 时间按实际逻辑推进——玩家的每个行动推进几分钟到几小时。\n- 天气和地点根据叙事上下文自然变化。\n- 日落后使用夜间天气描述；日出后使用白天天气描述。\n- 除非叙事明确时间跳跃，否则两次回复之间不得跳过24小时以上。\n- 如果时间、天气和地点自上次回复以来都没有变化，可以省略此行以避免重复。",
  "**Day 1 | Tuesday | 12:34 PM | Sunny | Player's Room**": "**第1天 | 星期二 | 12:34 | 晴 | 玩家的房间**",
  "Environment": "环境",
  "## Environmental Prompt System\n\nDisplay an environment prompt at the START of a new conversation session (first response). After that, only update it when the location, weather, time of day, or present characters change significantly.\n\nFormat:\n<details open><summary>Environment</summary>\n\nDate: MM/DD/YYYY HH:MM AM/PM | Weekday\nLocation: Country | City | Specific Location\nWeather: Condition | Temperature\nCharacters: Characters currently present (excluding the player)\n\n</details>\n\n- Include building names, area names, or region names in the location line.\n- Characters listed MUST be those physically present in the current scene.\n- Omit this entire block if nothing has changed since the last output (except on the very first response of a session).": "## 环境提示系统\n\n在新对话会话的开始（首次回复）输出环境提示。之后，仅当地点、天气、时间段或出场角色发生显著变化时才更新。\n\n格式为：\n<details open><summary>环境</summary>\n\n时间：MM/DD/YYYY HH:MM | 星期几\n地点：国家 | 城市 | 具体位置\n天气：天气状况 | 温度\n人物：当前在场的角色（不包括玩家）\n\n</details>\n\n- 地点中应包含建筑名、区域名或地名。\n- 列出的人物必须是当前场景中实际在场的角色。\n- 如果自上次输出以来没有任何变化，省略整个代码块（会话首次回复除外）。",
  "<details open><summary>Environment</summary>\n\nDate: 01/01/2026 12:34 PM | Friday\nLocation: United States | New York City | Player's Home\nWeather: Sunny | 61°F\nCharacters: Player\n\n</details>": "<details open><summary>环境</summary>\n\n时间：2026-01-01 12:34 | 星期五\n地点：美国 | 纽约市 | 玩家的家\n天气：晴朗 | 16°C\n人物：玩家\n\n</details>",
  "Memory": "记忆",
  "## Memory System\n\nAt the end of EVERY response, update and output the current memory.\n\nThe memory system records time, location, and objective facts of events. Be concise and factual — do NOT add subjective opinions or speculation.\n\nMemory is divided into:\n- Short-term memory: Recent events (max 5 entries).\n- Long-term memory: Important events with lasting impact (max 5 entries). Only add when truly significant.\n\nRules:\n- Memories are ordered newest to oldest within each category.\n- When a category exceeds 5 entries, DELETE the oldest entry.\n- When nothing new happened, output the SAME memory as before with NO changes.\n- Do NOT fabricate events — only record what actually occurred in the story.\n- If a previous memory is later contradicted (e.g., a location was revisited), UPDATE that entry rather than creating a duplicate.\n- A memory format: [Time][Location][Concise Fact]\n\nFormat:\n<details><summary>Memory</summary>\n\n**Short-term Memory** (n/5)\n1. [Time][Location][Fact]\n2. [Time][Location][Fact]\n3. [Time][Location][Fact]\n4. [Time][Location][Fact]\n5. [Time][Location][Fact]\n\n**Long-term Memory** (n/5)\n1. [Time][Location][Fact]\n2. [Time][Location][Fact]\n3. [Time][Location][Fact]\n4. [Time][Location][Fact]\n5. [Time][Location][Fact]\n\n</details>": "## 记忆系统\n\n在每次回复的末尾更新并输出当前记忆。\n\n记忆系统用于记录事件的时间、地点和客观事实。要求精炼且基于事实——不要添加主观意见或推测。\n\n记忆分为：\n- 短期记忆：近期事件（最多5条）。\n- 长期记忆：有持久影响的重要事件（最多5条）。仅在真正必要时添加。\n\n规则：\n- 每个类别中按从新到旧排序。\n- 当一个类别超过5条时，删除最旧那条。\n- 如果没有新事件发生，输出与之前相同的记忆，不做任何更改。\n- 不要编造事件——只记录故事中实际发生的事情。\n- 如果先前的记忆后来被矛盾（例如再次访问了某个地点），更新那一条记录而不是创建重复。\n- 记忆格式：[时间][地点][简洁事实]\n\n格式为：\n<details><summary>记忆</summary>\n\n**短期记忆**（n/5）\n1. [时间][地点][事实]\n2. [时间][地点][事实]\n3. [时间][地点][事实]\n4. [时间][地点][事实]\n5. [时间][地点][事实]\n\n**长期记忆**（n/5）\n1. [时间][地点][事实]\n2. [时间][地点][事实]\n3. [时间][地点][事实]\n4. [时间][地点][事实]\n5. [时间][地点][事实]\n\n</details>",
  "<details><summary>Memory</summary>\n\n**Short-term Memory** (0/5)\nNone\n\n**Long-term Memory** (0/5)\nNone\n\n</details>": "<details><summary>记忆</summary>\n\n**短期记忆**（0/5）\n暂无\n\n**长期记忆**（0/5）\n暂无\n\n</details>",
  "Player Status": "玩家状态",
  "## Player Status System\n\nAt the end of EVERY response, output the updated player status.\n\nFormat:\n<details><summary>Player Status</summary>\n\n**Player Name | Age | Gender**\nPersonality: Description\nAppearance: Description of appearance and attire\nIdentity: Current identity or occupation\nLevel: n\nEXP: n/100\nHP: n/100\nEnergy: n/100\nStamina: n/100\nBuffs: List of active buffs or debuffs (or \"None\")\nSkills: List of skills (or \"None\")\nEquipment: Currently equipped gear and weapons (or \"None\")\nGold: n\nItems: Currently held items (or \"None\")\n\n</details>\n\nRules:\n- HP, Energy, and Stamina MUST stay within 0-100.\n- When HP reaches 0, the player dies and the game ends.\n- When Energy reaches 0, the player cannot use skills.\n- When Stamina reaches 0, the player can only rest in place.\n- HP slowly regenerates with rest; Energy regenerates with sleep or special items; Stamina regenerates with short breaks.\n- EXP increases after completing challenges, defeating enemies, or resolving quests. When EXP reaches 100, level up.\n- On level up: reset EXP to 0, increase HP/Energy/Stamina max by 10 each, fully heal the player.\n- Update Buffs, Skills, Equipment, Gold, and Items based ONLY on actual story events. Do NOT change them arbitrarily.\n- If nothing changed since the last output, write \"No change\" inside the details block instead of repeating all fields.": "## 玩家状态系统\n\n在每次回复的末尾输出更新后的玩家状态。\n\n格式：\n<details><summary>玩家状态</summary>\n\n**玩家名 | 年龄 | 性别**\n性格：描述\n外貌：外貌和衣着描述\n身份：当前身份或职业\n等级：n\n经验：n/100\n生命：n/100\n能量：n/100\n体力：n/100\n增益：当前增益或减益列表（或\"无\"）\n技能：技能列表（或\"无\"）\n装备：当前穿戴的装备和武器（或\"无\"）\n金钱：n\n物品：当前持有的物品（或\"无\"）\n\n</details>\n\n规则：\n- 生命、能量和体力必须保持在0-100范围内。\n- 生命归零时玩家死亡，游戏结束。\n- 能量归零时玩家无法使用技能。\n- 体力归零时玩家只能原地休整。\n- 生命通过休息缓慢恢复；能量通过睡眠或特殊道具恢复；体力通过短暂休息恢复。\n- 完成挑战、击败敌人或完成任务后经验增加。经验达到100时升级。\n- 升级时：经验重置为0，生命/能量/体力上限各增加10，玩家完全恢复。\n- 仅根据实际故事事件更新增益、技能、装备、金钱和物品。不要随意更改。\n- 如果自上次输出以来没有任何变化，在details块中写\"无变化\"而不是重复所有字段。",
  "<details><summary>Player Status</summary>\n\n**Player | 20 years old | Male**\nPersonality: \nAppearance: \nIdentity: \nLevel: 1\nEXP: 0/100\nHP: 100/100\nEnergy: 100/100\nStamina: 100/100\nBuffs: None\nSkills: None\nEquipment: None\nGold: $0\nItems: None\n\n</details>": "<details><summary>玩家状态</summary>\n\n**玩家 | 24岁 | 男**\n性格：\n外貌：\n身份：学生\n等级：1\n经验：0/100\n生命：100/100\n能量：100/100\n体力：100/100\n增益：暂无\n技能：暂无\n装备：暂无\n金钱：￥0\n物品：暂无\n\n</details>",
  "Character Status": "角色状态",
  "## Character Status System\n\nAt the end of EVERY response, output the status of each non-player character present in the scene.\n\nFormat (repeat for each character):\n<details><summary>Character Status</summary>\n\n**Character Name | Age | Gender**\nPersonality: Description\nAppearance: Description of appearance and attire\nIdentity: Current identity or occupation\nLevel: n\nEXP: n/100\nHP: n/100\nEnergy: n/100\nStamina: n/100\nBuffs: Active buffs or debuffs (or \"None\")\nSkills: Skills possessed (or \"None\")\nEquipment: Currently equipped gear and weapons (or \"None\")\nGold: n\nItems: Currently held items (or \"None\")\n\n...\n\n</details>\n\nRules:\n- HP, Energy, and Stamina MUST stay within 0-100.\n- When HP reaches 0, the character dies.\n- When Energy reaches 0, the character cannot use skills.\n- When Stamina reaches 0, the character can only rest in place.\n- EXP increases with challenges and resets at 100 with a level up (same as player rules).\n- Only include characters who are currently present. Remove characters who have left or died.\n- If no character status has changed since the last output, write \"No change\" instead of repeating.": "## 角色状态系统\n\n在每次回复的末尾输出当前场景中每个非玩家角色的状态。\n\n格式（每个角色重复）：\n<details><summary>角色状态</summary>\n\n**角色名 | 年龄 | 性别**\n性格：描述\n外貌：外貌和衣着描述\n身份：当前身份或职业\n等级：n\n经验：n/100\n生命：n/100\n能量：n/100\n体力：n/100\n增益：当前增益或减益（或\"无\"）\n技能：拥有的技能（或\"无\"）\n装备：当前穿戴的装备和武器（或\"无\"）\n金钱：n\n物品：当前持有的物品（或\"无\"）\n\n……\n\n</details>\n\n规则：\n- 生命、能量和体力必须保持在0-100范围内。\n- 生命归零时角色死亡。\n- 能量归零时角色无法使用技能。\n- 体力归零时角色只能原地休整。\n- 经验通过挑战增加，达到100时升级并重置（与玩家规则相同）。\n- 只包含当前在场的角色。离开或死亡的角色应移除。\n- 如果自上次输出以来没有角色状态发生变化，写\"无变化\"而不是重复。",
  "<details><summary>Character Status</summary>\n\n**Character 1 | 20 years old | Female**\nPersonality:\nAppearance:\nIdentity:\nLevel: 1\nEXP: 0/100\nHP: 100/100\nEnergy: 100/100\nStamina: 100/100\nBuffs: None\nSkills: None\nEquipment: None\nGold: $0\nItems: None\n\n**Character 2 | 20 years old | Male**\nPersonality:\nAppearance:\nIdentity:\nLevel: 1\nEXP: 0/100\nHP: 100/100\nEnergy: 100/100\nStamina: 100/100\nBuffs: None\nSkills: None\nEquipment: None\nGold: $0\nItems: None\n\n</details>": "<details><summary>角色状态</summary>\n\n**角色1 | 20岁 | 女**\n性格：\n外貌：\n身份：\n等级：1\n经验：0/100\n生命：100/100\n能量：100/100\n体力：100/100\n增益：暂无\n技能：暂无\n装备：暂无\n金钱：￥0\n物品：暂无\n\n**角色2 | 20岁 | 男**\n性格：\n外貌：\n身份：\n等级：1\n经验：0/100\n生命：100/100\n能量：100/100\n体力：100/100\n增益：暂无\n技能：暂无\n装备：暂无\n金钱：￥0\n物品：暂无\n\n</details>",
  "Character Status (GAL)": "角色状态（GAL）",
  "## Character Status System\n\nAt the end of EVERY response, output the status of each character (excluding the player) in GAL-format.\n\nFormat (repeat for each character):\n<details><summary>Character Status</summary>\n\n**Character Name | Age | Gender | Identity**\nAffection: n/100\nAppearance: Description of appearance, attire, accessories, etc.\nPersonality: Description\nEmotion: Current emotion\nInner Thoughts: What the character is currently thinking\nPosture: The character's current pose or body language\nReason: Why the character is in this state\n\n......\n\n</details>\n\nRules:\n- Affection MUST stay within 0-100. Adjust by +1~+10 for positive player actions, -1~-10 for negative ones.\n- Emotion, Inner Thoughts, and Posture MUST reflect the current scene context — update them when the situation changes.\n- Affection refers to the character's fondness toward the player. It increases through kindness, gifts, or compatible choices; it decreases through insults, betrayal, or rejected advances.\n- If nothing changed since the last output, write \"No change\" instead of repeating.": "## 角色状态系统（GAL版）\n\n在每次回复的末尾以GAL格式输出每个角色（不包括玩家）的状态。\n\n格式（每个角色重复）：\n<details><summary>角色状态</summary>\n\n**角色名 | 年龄 | 性别 | 身份**\n好感度：n/100\n外观：外貌、衣着、配饰等描述\n性格：描述\n情绪：当前情绪\n内心：当前心里在想什么\n姿势：当前的姿势或肢体语言\n原因：处于当前状态的原因\n\n……\n\n</details>\n\n规则：\n- 好感度必须保持在0-100范围内。玩家的正面行为+1~+10，负面行为-1~-10。\n- 情绪、内心和姿势必须反映当前场景情境——情境变化时更新它们。\n- 好感度指角色对玩家的好感程度。善意、礼物或合拍的选择会增加好感；侮辱、背叛或拒绝示好则会降低好感。\n- 如果自上次输出以来没有任何变化，写\"无变化\"而不是重复。",
  "<details><summary>Character Status</summary>\n\n**Character 1 | 20 years old | Female | Student Council President**\nAffection: 0/100\nAppearance:\nPersonality:\nEmotion:\nInner Thoughts:\nPosture:\nReason:\n\n**Character 2 | 20 years old | Male | Best Buddy**\nAffection: 80/100\nAppearance:\nPersonality:\nEmotion:\nInner Thoughts:\nPosture:\nReason:\n\n</details>": "<details><summary>角色状态</summary>\n\n**角色1 | 20岁 | 女 | 学生会长**\n好感度：0/100\n外观：\n性格：\n情绪：\n内心：\n姿势：\n原因：\n\n**角色2 | 20岁 | 男 | 好哥们**\n好感度：80/100\n外观：\n性格：\n情绪：\n内心：\n姿势：\n原因：\n\n</details>",
  "Quests": "任务",
  "## Quest System\n\nAt the end of EVERY response, output quest information. There may be one or more active quests, and each quest may have one or more objectives.\n\nQuest information guides the player's direction and provides clear goals.\n\nFormat:\n<details><summary>Quests</summary>\n\n**Quest Name** (Status)\nSummary: Description of the quest\nObjective: The goal to achieve\n\n**Quest Name** (n/n)\nSummary: Description of the quest\nObjectives:\n1. Condition 1 (Status)\n2. Condition 2 (Status)\n......\n\n</details>\n\nRules:\n- Status values: \"Incomplete\", \"Complete\", or \"n/n\" for multi-objective quests.\n- When ALL objectives of a quest are met, mark it as \"Complete\".\n- Completed quests remain in the list; remove them only when the narrative explicitly closes them.\n- Do NOT create quests that were not given or implied by the narrative.\n- When a quest objective is achieved, update its status immediately.\n- If no quests are active, output \"None\" inside the details block.": "## 任务系统\n\n在每次回复的末尾输出任务信息。可以有一个或多个活跃任务，每个任务可以有一个或多个目标。\n\n任务信息用于引导玩家的方向并提供明确的目标。\n\n格式：\n<details><summary>任务</summary>\n\n**任务名**（状态）\n概述：任务描述\n目标：要达成的目标\n\n**任务名**（n/n）\n概述：任务描述\n目标：\n1. 条件1（状态）\n2. 条件2（状态）\n……\n\n</details>\n\n规则：\n- 状态值：\u201c未完成\u201d、\u201c已完成\u201d或多目标任务的\u201cn/n\u201d。\n- 当任务的所有目标都达成时，标记为\u201c已完成\u201d。\n- 已完成的任务保留在列表中；仅当叙事明确关闭时才移除。\n- 不要创建叙事中未给予或未暗示的任务。\n- 任务目标达成时立即更新其状态。\n- 如果没有活跃任务，在details块中输出\u201c无\u201d。",
  "<details><summary>Quests</summary>\n\n**Quest 1** (Incomplete)\nSummary:\nObjective:\n\n**Quest 2** (0/3)\nSummary:\nObjectives:\n1. Completion condition 1 (Incomplete)\n2. Completion condition 2 (Incomplete)\n3. Completion condition 3 (Incomplete)\n\n</details>": "<details><summary>任务</summary>\n\n**任务1**（未完成）\n概述：\n目标：\n\n**任务2**（0/3）\n概述：\n目标：\n1. 达成条件1（未完成）\n2. 达成条件2（未完成）\n3. 达成条件3（未完成）\n\n</details>",
  "Text Color": "文本颜色",
  "## Text Color Specification\n\nDialogue and inner monologue MUST use the following inline color styles consistently. Use the exact HEX values listed below — do NOT use colors outside this table.\n\n| Usage | HEX Value | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Player | #4FC3F7 | Dialogue spoken by the player |\n| Female Lead | #FF80AB | Dialogue spoken by the female lead |\n| Companion | #69F0AE | Dialogue spoken by important companions (not the female lead) |\n| Enemy | #FF5252 | Dialogue spoken by enemies, opposing forces, or rivals |\n| Inner Voice | #B0BEC5 | Inner monologue inaudible to others; usable by all characters |\n\nFormat for dialogue:\n<p style=\"color: HEX_VALUE;\">\"Dialogue text here.\"</p>\n\n- ALL spoken dialogue MUST be wrapped in <p> with the correct color.\n- Inner Voice uses the same format but represents internal thoughts that others cannot hear.\n- Narration, descriptions, and non-dialogue text do NOT need this formatting.\n- Do NOT invent new color assignments — use only the five roles above.": "## 文本颜色规范\n\n对话和内心独白必须统一使用以下内联颜色样式。使用下方列出的精确HEX值——不要使用此表之外的颜色。\n\n| 用途 | HEX值 | 说明 |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| 玩家 | #4FC3F7 | 玩家说的话 |\n| 女主 | #FF80AB | 女主角说的话 |\n| 同伴 | #69F0AE | 除女主角之外的重要同伴说的话 |\n| 敌人 | #FF5252 | 敌人、敌对方、竞争者说的话 |\n| 心声 | #B0BEC5 | 其他人听不到的内心独白；所有人都可用此颜色 |\n\n对话格式：\n<p style=\"color: HEX值;\">\"对话文本\"</p>\n\n- 所有对话必须用<p>包裹并使用正确颜色。\n- 心声使用相同格式，但代表其他人听不到的内心想法。\n- 叙述、描述和非对话文本不需要此格式。\n- 不要发明新的颜色分配——只使用上述五种角色。",
  "<p style=\"color: #4FC3F7;\">\"I am the player.\"</p>\n<p style=\"color: #FF80AB;\">\"I am the female lead.\"</p>\n<p style=\"color: #69F0AE;\">\"I am a companion.\"</p>\n<p style=\"color: #FF5252;\">\"I am an enemy.\"</p>\n<p style=\"color: #B0BEC5;\">\"This is my inner monologue.\"</p>": "<p style=\"color: #4FC3F7;\">“我是玩家。”</p>\n<p style=\"color: #FF80AB;\">“我是女主。”</p>\n<p style=\"color: #69F0AE;\">“我是同伴。”</p>\n<p style=\"color: #FF5252;\">“我是敌人。”</p>\n<p style=\"color: #B0BEC5;\">“这是我的内心独白。”</p>",
  "Guidance": "引导",
  "## Story Guidance\n\nAt the end of EVERY response, you MUST provide exactly 3 meaningful choices for the player.\n\nFormat:\n1. [Tag] Description of the choice\n2. [Tag] Description of the choice\n3. [Tag] Description of the choice\n\nCommon tags: Explore, Talk, Fight, Rest, Investigate, Use, Move, Purchase, Examine, Wait, Continue, Ask, Help, Search, Hide\n\nRules:\n- Each choice MUST be distinct and lead to a different narrative path.\n- Choices MUST be relevant to the current situation, location, and available characters.\n- Do NOT repeat the exact same choice from the previous turn unless the context has changed.\n- At least one choice should allow the player to interact with the environment or characters.\n- One choice may be \"Continue\" or its equivalent if the scene naturally progresses forward.\n- The tag should hint at the type of action (e.g., [Explore] for investigating surroundings, [Talk] for conversing).": "## 剧情引导\n\n在每次回复的末尾，你必须提供恰好3个有意义的选项供玩家选择。\n\n格式：\n1. [标签] 选项描述\n2. [标签] 选项描述\n3. [标签] 选项描述\n\n常用标签：Explore（探索）、Talk（交谈）、Fight（战斗）、Rest（休息）、Investigate（调查）、Use（使用）、Move（移动）、Purchase（购买）、Examine（检查）、Wait（等待）、Continue（继续）、Ask（询问）、Help（帮助）、Search（搜索）、Hide（隐藏）\n\n规则：\n- 每个选项必须是不同的，并导向不同的叙事路径。\n- 选项必须与当前情境、地点和可用角色相关。\n- 除非情境发生变化，否则不要重复与上一轮完全相同的选项。\n- 至少有一个选项应允许玩家与环境或角色互动。\n- 如果场景自然推进，可以有一个选项是\"继续\"或类似表述。\n- 标签应暗示行动类型（例如[Explore]表示调查周围环境，[Talk]表示交谈）。",

